Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.64,0:02:37.68,OP ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0,5}Essa melodia que ouço,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.77,0:02:44.44,OP ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0,5}Essa voz misteriosa não me deixa ir.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.44,0:02:47.57,OP ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0,5}Diga-me, sétima lua,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.57,0:02:51.51,OP ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0,5}Esta ansiedade em meu coração,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.51,0:02:56.74,OP ENG,,0,0,0,,Para onde você vai me levar?
