Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.67,0:03:03.40,OP ENG,,0,0,0,,No ritmo ecoante,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.40,0:03:12.81,OP ENG,,0,0,0,,Ainda procuro uma resposta para a dança louca.
