Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:36.35,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Eu quero continuar procurando por isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:44.63,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Não é um sonho que qualquer pessoa possa ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:48.62,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Mesmo que seja uma ilusão,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:52.74,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Eu a encontrarei com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.48,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Crendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:19:00.81,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Continuarei caminhando.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.08,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Enquanto...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:17.28,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Não desistirei, nem mesmo diante de uma luz fraca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:20.75,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Até que um poder invisível
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:25.18,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}acorde dentro de mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:29.77,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Eu vou continuar seguindo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.27,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}essa estrada que leva longe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:19.46,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Para sempre...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.06,0:32:07.14,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Pegando uma estrela cadente,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.14,0:32:11.20,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Eu passei por um buraco negro.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.20,0:32:15.24,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Quando fui atingido pela chuva torrencial,{Note: "ame ni utare" means "hit by the rain", not "sing in the rain" as AnaF seems to translate it as - "utare" is in hiragana and not kanji, so it doesn't have a specific interpretation, which might have caused this confusion.}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.24,0:32:18.82,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Eu chorei de solidão, mas
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.38,0:32:24.28,FitD ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur0.3}Não consegui esquecer aquela música de amor.
